Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Characterization' tab

When I select 'Emphysema' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding button' is enabled
And 'Centrilobular' radio button is enabled
And 'Paraseptal' radio button is enabled
And 'Panlobular' radio button is enabled
And 'Bullous' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Centrilobular' radio button
Then 'Confluent emphysema (advanced destructive)' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Bullous' radio button
Then 'Diameter largest bulla' input field is enabled
